summary: This mod aims to merge the world of The Elder Scrolls Franchise with that of Dishonored. It features a a small quest along with the supernatural abilities gifted to Corvo by the outsider. It is currently in Alpha.
descriptionHtml:
[CENTER][SIZE=+10][COLOR=Lightseagreen][B]GIFTS OF THE OUTSIDER[/B][/COLOR][/SIZE][/CENTER]

[CENTER][SIZE=+2][COLOR=RED]I have released the full version of this mod. please follow to link to download the full version: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/35564//?]Gifts of the outsider[/url][/COLOR][/SIZE][/CENTER]
